---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About - Nithil R (Huxley)"
  description="About Nithil R - physics student, generalist, and explorer of interesting problems"
>
  <Header />
  
  <main class="main-content">
    <div class="container">
      <article class="about-content">
        <h1 class="page-title">about</h1>
        
        <div class="content-body">
          <p><strong>Nithil R (Huxley)</strong></p>
          <p>I'm a physics student.<br>I'm interested in most things.</p>

          <p>In a past life, I was a numismatist, stockpicker, runner, pyromaniac, cartographer and cryptographer.</p>

          <p>Today, I work on interesting problems in a wide variety of fields. If your work lies on the bleeding edge of human endeavour, I'm probably interested in you and what you have to say.</p>

          <p>Here's what's currently keeping me up at night:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>External frameworks that maximize accountability and transparency in systems of governance designed to minimize it</li>
            <li>CTOL/HTOL autonomization</li>
            <li>What the framing, modelling, and discovery of physical laws might look like in the context of autonomous, evolutionarily distinct, genetically unweighted synthetic intelligences.</li>
          </ul>

          <p>If this is interesting to you, reach me here: <a href="mailto:hi@nithil.xyz">hi@nithil.xyz</a></p>

          <h2>contact</h2>
          <ul class="contact-list">
            <li>Email: <a href="mailto:hi@nithil.xyz">hi@nithil.xyz</a></li>
            <li>Twitter: Huggslie</li>
            <li>Discord: lanraev</li>
          </ul>

          <p>This site is a public-facing repository of my thoughts and works, and a window into what I'm currently interested in.</p>

          <p>To know more about me (in a more personal light), go <a href="https://www.nithil.xyz/about/">here</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .main-content {
    flex: 1;
  }
  
  .container {
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--space-lg);
  }
  
  .about-content {
    max-width: 100%;
  }
  
  .page-title {
    font-family: var(--font-family-mono);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-2xl);
    text-transform: lowercase;
  }
  
  .content-body {
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  .content-body p {
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-lg);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }
  
  .content-body h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-family-mono);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: var(--space-2xl) 0 var(--space-lg);
    text-transform: lowercase;
  }
  
  .content-body ul {
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-lg);
    padding-left: var(--space-xl);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }
  
  .content-body li {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }
  
  .content-body a {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  
  .content-body a:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent-hover);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  
  .content-body strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  
  .contact-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding-left: 0;
  }
  
  .contact-list li {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .container {
      padding: var(--space-xl) var(--space-md);
    }
  }
</style>
